# Tic Tac Toe Game

Welcome to the Tic Tac Toe Game project! This is a classic game where two players take turns marking spaces in a 3x3 grid, aiming to get three of their symbols (either "X" or "O") in a row, column, or diagonal.

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Features

- **Two-player Mode**: Play against a friend locally, taking turns on the same device.
- **Responsive Design**: The game is designed to work on various screen sizes, from desktop to mobile.
- **Win Detection**: The game detects when a player has won or when it's a draw.
- **Reset Button**: Easily restart the game to play again.

